  "original_title": "\u0d95\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 17\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "17 who were going to Australia were caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "17 people who tried to go to Australia illegally by sea have been arrested by the Special Task Force at Punnakkudi beach in Eraur.",
        "The raid was carried out according to information that a group of people were staying at the coast to go abroad by sea.",
        "The person who supported it has also been taken into custody by the police, along with Rs. 17, 10,000 and a van carrying the group.",
        "The arrested persons are residents of Mulathivu Peduruthuduwa Jaffna Kilinochchi and Velwetitura",
        "Along with them, the Special Task Force has taken over 17 lakh rupees in cash and a van that transported the people.",
        "The Special Task Force says that there were 16 men and one woman among the group."
      ],
